commitResults.messageTitle: Added start method to greet, echo, and handle exit commands
Added taskList to store tasks and list function
Created Task class, allow marking as done and undone
Added Todo, Deadline, and Event classes
Set up test case for runtest.bat

commitResults.messageBody:
Task data is lost between Duke sessions.

Users will want to keep their task data without running Duke 24/7.

Let's
* automatically store task data into a data.txt file whenever the task
list changes
* allow users to load tasks from a specified file on start-up, with the
default being data.txt

commitResults.messageTitle: Enforce datetime input with time zone for Deadline and Event
commitResults.messageBody:
Duke accepts any string as a datetime qualifier.

Standardising the datetime input will keep task descriptions clean and
allow them to be compared with each other.

Let's
* ask the user for their time zone before starting Duke
* store datetime qualifiers as ZonedDateTime instances in Deadline and
Event instances
